Detailed Description

template<class ObjectType>
class stGenericPriorityQueue< ObjectType >

This class implements a global priority queue based on chained list used for the Incremental Nearest Neighbor.

This priority queue is implemented using a simple chained list. This implementation of priority queue is based on the paper "Incremental Similarity Search in Multimedia Databases" - G. R. Hjaltason & Hanan Samet - 2000.

Author:
Marcos Rodrigues Vieira
Version:
1.0
